tribution with altitude. Haze particles settle out of the\natmosphere and onto Pluto's surface, at a rate sufficient to alter surface\noptical properties on seasonal time scales. Pluto's regional scale albedo\ncontrasts may be preserved in the face of the haze deposition by atmospheric\ncollapse.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 24 Feb 2017 21:26:23 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 28 Feb 2017 14:53:57 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-03-15"}
